      <title>韩国主要反对党支持取消资本利得税计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/korea-s-main-opposition-backs-plan-to-drop-capital-gains-tax</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国主要反对党将支持政府放弃对散户投资者金融投资征收资本利得税的决定，从而放弃数月来对这一有争议举措的抗议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/korea-s-main-opposition-backs-plan-to-drop-capital-gains-tax</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 02:02:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元下跌，债券期货上涨，因特朗普部分交易被削减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/dollar-falls-bond-futures-gain-as-some-trump-trades-are-pared</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于周二美国大选前的民意调查数据促使一些投资者削减所谓的特朗普交易，美元指数出现自 9 月底以来的最大跌幅，美国国债期货上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/dollar-falls-bond-futures-gain-as-some-trump-trades-are-pared</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 01:38:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伯克希尔现金储备创历史新高，巴菲特继续减持苹果股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-04/warren-buffett-keeps-cutting-apple-stake-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于沃伦·巴菲特继续避免进行重大收购，伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司的现金储备在第三季度达到创纪录的 3252 亿美元。与此同时，该集团还再次减持了苹果的股份，这次减持了约 25%。财经编辑亚当·海格在“彭博社：亚洲交易”中进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-04/warren-buffett-keeps-cutting-apple-stake-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 01:34:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克与特朗普的关系让习近平有了一位有影响力的朋友</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-04/musk-s-ties-with-trump-gives-xi-an-influential-friend-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果前美国总统埃隆·马斯克重获白宫控制权，他将成为唐纳德·特朗普竞选活动的主要捐助者之一，这对中国国家主席习近平来说是个好兆头。这位特斯拉和 SpaceX 的亿万富翁首席执行官已向特朗普捐赠了 1 亿多美元，并与北京有着广泛的商业利益。中国政府记者科伦·墨菲在“彭博社：亚洲贸易”中进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-04/musk-s-ties-with-trump-gives-xi-an-influential-friend-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 01:33:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>GLP 取消债券发售 聚焦长期融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/glp-s-canceled-bond-sale-shows-worries-over-finances-persist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲主要物流运营商 GLP Pte 在阔别债券市场三年之后放弃重返债券市场的尝试，尽管该公司最近努力出售资产并削减债务，但人们仍对该公司财务状况感到担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/glp-s-canceled-bond-sale-shows-worries-over-finances-persist</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 00:34:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>B. Riley 支持的特许经营集团申请破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/b-riley-backed-franchise-group-files-for-bankruptcy-protection-m327xjyp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旗下拥有 Vitamin Shoppe 和 Pet Supplies Plus 等品牌的 Franchise Group Inc. 在其创始人和支持者 B. Riley Financial Inc. 经历数月亏损和动荡后申请破产保护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/b-riley-backed-franchise-group-files-for-bankruptcy-protection-m327xjyp</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 23:23:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国希望看到谁入主白宫？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-03/who-china-want-to-see-next-in-the-white-house</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贸易争端、关税和台湾问题——这三个问题一直是中美关系紧张的核心。随着美国总统大选接近尾声，这种复杂关系的未来悬而未决。彭博社的斯蒂芬·恩格尔报道了这场选举将如何重塑世界两大经济体之间的关系。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-03/who-china-want-to-see-next-in-the-white-house</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 23:16:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 推迟增产且伊朗加强言论，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OPEC+同意将12月份的增产计划推迟一个月且中东紧张局势再度升级，推动油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 23:10:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：美国民意调查显示没有明确领导者，美元走弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/dollar-weakens-as-us-polls-signal-no-clear-leader-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元下跌，因为投资者放弃了对唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国总统大选的押注，因为最新的一系列民意调查数据显示特朗普没有明显优势。OPEC+推迟增产后，油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/dollar-weakens-as-us-polls-signal-no-clear-leader-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 22:45:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚利率下滑，西太平洋银行 2025 年面临艰难处境；股价波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/westpac-profit-tops-estimates-as-bank-increases-share-buyback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西太平洋银行 (Westpac Banking Corp.) 的股票回购增加抵消了人们对费用的担忧以及明年澳大利亚利率下调的潜在影响，导致其股价出现波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/westpac-profit-tops-estimates-as-bank-increases-share-buyback</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 20:39:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
